  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2><br><strong>The Party of Demons</strong> is a high pace, competition bullet hell game. It contains well-designed bullets and awesome background music. You can even compete with your friend in this game.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>well-designed Bullets.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can compete with your friend in this game.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>13 original background music.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>14 unique characters with different magic skills.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 difficulty options. Everyone can have fun in it.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How To Play</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dodge the bullets on the screen</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/3da4f4101df64306defdc247423b55aa.poster.avif?t=1547796038\" width=194 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/3da4f4101df64306defdc247423b55aa.webm?t=1547796038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/3da4f4101df64306defdc247423b55aa.mp4?t=1547796038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shoot the birds to gain mana and cast bullets on your rival's screen.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/d77f79e5f1140d2d1fb5ab1681728221.poster.avif?t=1547796038\" width=130 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/d77f79e5f1140d2d1fb5ab1681728221.webm?t=1547796038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/d77f79e5f1140d2d1fb5ab1681728221.mp4?t=1547796038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chant and release magic to defend/attack</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/ec1e090dd67ffd2424833b98ecfa8c1d.poster.avif?t=1547796038\" width=138 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/ec1e090dd67ffd2424833b98ecfa8c1d.webm?t=1547796038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/ec1e090dd67ffd2424833b98ecfa8c1d.mp4?t=1547796038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Whoever stand the last wins</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How To Control</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Keyboard:</li></ul>Move: up, down, left, right<br>Slowdown: left shift<br>Chant/Release magic: Z<br>Burst rune: X<br>Fire/Hold fire: C<br>Select rune: A, S<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gamepad:</li></ul>Move: left stick<br>Slowdown: A<br>Chant/Release magic: X<br>Burst rune: B<br>Fire/Hold fire: Y<br>Select rune: left shoulder, right shoulder<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mouse:</li></ul>Move: Move the mouse<br>Slowdown: left key<br>Chant/Release magic: right key<br>Burst rune: middle key<br>Fire/Hold fire: you cannot hold fire when using a mouse<br>Select rune: wheel up, wheel down",
