1140d2d1fb5ab1681728221.mp4?t=1547796038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chant and release magic to defend/attack</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/ec1e090dd67ffd2424833b98ecfa8c1d.poster.avif?t=1547796038\" width=138 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/ec1e090dd67ffd2424833b98ecfa8c1d.webm?t=1547796038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930860/extras/ec1e090dd67ffd2424833b98ecfa8c1d.mp4?t=1547796038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Whoever stand the last wins</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How To Control</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Keyboard:</li></ul>Move: up, down, left, right<br>Slowdown: left shift<br>Chant/Release magic: Z<br>Burst rune: X<br>Fire/Hold fire: C<br>Select rune: A, S<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gamepad:</li></ul>Move: left stick<br>Slowdown: A<br>Chant/Release magic: X<br>Burst rune: B<br>Fire/Hold fire: Y<br>Select rune: left shoulder, right shoulder<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mouse:</li></ul>Move: Move the mouse<br>Slowdown: left key<br>Chant/Release magic: right key<br>Burst rune: middle key<br>Fire/Hold fire: you cannot hold fire when using a mouse<br>Select rune: wheel up, wheel down",
